# Title: NtdllPipe Like Activity Execution
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-03-05
# Level: high
# Description: Detects command that type the content of ntdll.dll to a different file or a pipe in order to evade AV / EDR detection. As seen being used in the POC NtdllPipe
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_cmd_ntdllpipe_redirect.yml

CommandLine IN ("*type %windir%\\system32\\ntdll.dll*", "*type %systemroot%\\system32\\ntdll.dll*", "*type c:\\windows\\system32\\ntdll.dll*", "*\\ntdll.dll > \\\\.\\pipe\\*")